## Acceptance Validation

Validates checkbox acceptance (terms of service).

```ruby
class User < ApplicationRecord
  # Checkbox must be checked
  validates :terms_of_service, acceptance: true
  
  # Custom values
  validates :privacy_policy, acceptance: { 
    accept: ['yes', '1', true]
  }
  
  # With custom message
  validates :terms, acceptance: { 
    message: "must be accepted to continue"
  }
end
```

